Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' before transitioning to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total duration of all instances of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' within a case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Average delay before starting 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' after 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in any case
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in any case
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases that also include 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Total time spent in 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' across all cases in the log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Average time from the start of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' to the end of the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases that were completed within the top 25% of performance times
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases with 'Completed + In Call' versus without
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Time from the completion of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' to the start of 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases that exceed the average case duration
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases with a high frequency of activity transitions before reaching 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Median duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' across all cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Difference in average duration between 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' to the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Variation in duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' across different organizations (grouped by 'organization country')
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Correlation between the duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the total case duration
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Distribution of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' durations across all cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' during different times of the year (seasonality analysis)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
